<template>
  <button @click="addCounter">{{ counterValue }}</button>
</template>

<script>
export default {
    name : "Globalcomponent",
    props : ['initialtest'],
    data () {
        return {
            counterValue : this["initialtest"]
        }
    },
    methods:{
        addCounter () {
            this.counterValue += 1;
        }
    }
}
</script>

<style>

</style>
